description: A) Works to 1x sycamore (T4) covered by LBE ORDER NO 18 (2) 1976: fellB) Works to trees covered by LBE ORDER NO 18 (2) 1976: 1x lime (T2): remove epicormic basal growth, reduce crown up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m, 1x false acacia (T3): remove epicormic basal growth, reduce crown up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m, 1x sycamore (T5): remove epicormic basal growth, reduce crown by up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m, 1x lime (T6): remove epicormic basal growth, reduce crown by up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m, 1x sycamore (T7): reduce crown by up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m, 1x lime (T8): remove epicormic basal growth and reduce crown up to 3m, crown lift to 3.5m.
